resource.q3a_verbatim: not disorganized but signage for directions could be more clear friendly staff
you guys need space after security theres no room to put your shoes back on

there is some room for improvement i think notes about how to prepare for general checkpoint should be at the entry area rather than right before where you load your bags didnt hear any music maybe ceiling music might help
there was a very short wait for security and still two lines to get everyone through staff was more friendly than at other airports
just standard airport didnt notice anything bad or good
need more lines to process people quicker

no body scan machines are at or close to tsa precheck lines which is not helpful and very unaccommodating to those traveling alone i have complained to tsa directly on one occasion and to the airline i use but have yet to see any improvement over a twoyear period of time i fly in and out of this terminal regularly and find reagan ohare and portland or all much more efficient and pleasant both in logistics and passenger satisfactionhelpfulness
overall solid thanks to the team

one of my bags was pulled aside no one mentioned it i looked and saw it since it did not come through i had to ask an agent if she could get my bag she directed me to stand at the screening station while she got the bag and searched it she pulled out a bottle of water i had forgotten was in there did not say anything except would i like to go back out then after i said no she asked me if i wanted to repack my bag i said yes and she walked away not very friendly
the airport checkpoint was not very busy the tsa precheck line went quickly staff were very nice
lines are confusing limited direction on which line to join after id check podium

the reason for the lower score is the length of time it took to get through everyone was very friendly and seemed focused and on task however the line was very short and it took a very long time for relatively few people to get through security i actually thought if this was a busy time of day travelers would get irritated thank you all for your work
speed and efficiency simplicity and organization
poor informationincorrect id is currently not invalid
time it took to get through security and could have had some areas to repack
standardized decent customer service safety is everyones concern
entry staff are good but waiting time is poor
overall experience was very smooth and fast
tsa pre staff was nicer than other airports helped push luggage through the xray machine
overall experience today was positive the checkpoint entry staff was rather distracted and inattentive and i had to get their attention to check my ticket before moving on
great experience everyone was very friendly smiling helpful
there were checkin stations not operating this is typical in all us airports i have been
i was through security in less than minutes
there were five of us in a row selected for random screening
so much gum on the carpet lines are confusing very nice staff
efficient clear plus tsa helps staff very professional
usually go through precheck and its just easier
had wheelchair service attendant was very helpful
i had clear which made the process very quick and easy no complaints except not much space to sit and put shoes on after security
im tsa precheck and clear so pretty fast logjam of bags after screening always
overall an excellent experience in the morning
they should have informed people prior to scan that they could leave their shoes on the canine sniff is unnecessary these two things caused a massive waitqueue
felt safe very efficient today it was faster than usual
the tsa personnel were focused and paying attention they were very helpful to passengers needing help without being rude or condescending
uh might have been nice if people will be a bit cheerier and looked us in the eye now and then

i arrive at sfo with some anxiety because things are always changing in airports since but it went very smoothly today when i was momentarily confused at the clear station there was someone soon at my side with guidance well done
i truly have no issues i like this airport cleanliness staff layout
staff was mostly handsoff with helping organize screening traffic time could be saved if tsa agents used verbal commands to help the flow of traffic
staff was generally rude said things like i dont care i just need you to move through gogo do not do that just generally rude
it can be very crowded at times and hard to move around
we were lucky enough to breeze through without much of a line a very smooth process
